@page "/components/layouts/static-box"
@attribute [LayoutKey("Demo.Box")]
@inherits PageBase

<h1>[LayoutKey("Demo.Box")] — static</h1>

<p>
    This page is rendered inside <code>DemoBoxLayout</code> purely because of the
    <code>[LayoutKey("Demo.Box")]</code> attribute on the class. There is <em>no</em>
    <code>@@layout</code> directive in this file and the page's compiled type carries
    no compile-time reference to <code>DemoBoxLayout</code> — the resolver looked the
    key up in <code>ILayoutRegistry</code> at render time.
</p>

<p>
    Note that <strong>none</strong> of the usual chrome (top nav, side menu, footer)
    is present — that's because the layout-by-key resolution wins over the Site
    default <code>MainLayout</code>.
</p>

<p>
    <a href="/components/layouts">← Back</a>
</p>
